1ST QUARTER 
Scoring summary 
PSU : FG Julius 33, 11:32. Drive: Six plays, 61 yards, 2:26. Key plays: Lynch 11 run for first down at PSU 34; Godwin 45 pass from Hackenberg for first down at OSU 21; the OSU defense bowed up there and Hackenberg threw incomplete on third-and-5. Penn State 3, Ohio State 0 
>> Click for details on how to win tickets and trips to OSU games from  Dispatch  Reader Rewards 
 
2ND QUARTER 
Scoring summary 
OSU : Barrett 5 run (Willoughby kick), 13:43. Drive: Ten plays, 70 yards, 3:56. Key plays: Miller 17 pass from Jones on third-and-11 from the OSU 40; Miller 15 run for first down at the Penn State 28; Barrett 12 run on third-and-7 from the 25; Barrett scored on a second-and-2 play after faking to Elliott and cutting left behind Vannett’s block. Ohio State 7, Penn State 3 
OSU : Elliott 10 run (Willoughby kick), 9:26. Drive: Five plays, 45 yards, 1:59. Key plays: Gulla 32 punt gave OSU first down at the Penn State 45; Thomas 8 pass from Jones for first down the 30; Miller runs of 8 and 12 yards for first down at the 10; on the next play, Elliott swept right and eluded four tacklers on the way to the end zone. Ohio State 14, Penn State 3 
OSU: Barrett 13 run (Willoughby kick), 3:17. Drive: Six plays, 66 yards, 2:37. Key plays: Elliott runs of 9 and 9 yards for first down at the Penn State 48; Miller 17 pass from Jones for first down at the 31; Elliott 15 run for first down at the 16; on second-and-7, Barrett went right on a well-executed option and jumped into the end zone as Thomas held his block. Ohio State 21, Penn State 3 
 
3RD QUARTER 
Scoring summary 
PSU : Hamilton 8 pass from Hackenberg (Julius kick), 13:59. Drive: Three plays, 78 yards, 1:01. Key plays: Godwin 56 pass from Hackenberg for first down at OSU 22; Barkley 14 run for first-and-goal at the 8; on the next play, Hackenberg threw a screen right to Hamilton, who avoided Bell’s tackle attempt and dived at the pylon. Ohio State 21, Penn State 10 


4TH QUARTER 
Scoring summary 
OSU : FG Willoughby 39, 12:54. Drive: Eleven plays, 53 yards, 5:12. Key plays: Barrett 6 run on third-and-4 from the OSU 31; Barrett net 11 run (after holding call) gave OSU first down at its 48; Barrett 27 run on third-and-10 from the 48; Willoughby came on after three plays netted 3 yards. Ohio State 24, Penn State 10 
OSU : Miller 5 pass from Barrett (Willoughby kick), 6:25. Drive: Eight plays, 85 yards, 3:35. Key plays: Elliott run of 19 yards, Barrett run of 13 and Elliott run of 15 on consecutive plays for first down at the Penn State 38; Samuel 21 pass from Barrett for first-and-goal at the 7; on second down, Barrett faked a run into the center of the line and threw a jump pass to the open Miller. Ohio State 31, Penn State 10 
OSU : Thomas 6 pass from Barrett (Willoughby kick), 4:14. Drive: Three plays, 22 yards, 1:01. Key plays: Hubbard recovery of Hackenberg fumble gave OSU possession at Penn State 22; Marshall 15 run for first down at the 7; on second-and-goal, Barrett lofted left to Thomas, who made a fine catch. Ohio State 38, Penn State 10
